text: One hardworking uncle Philip Lim and another carpenter savvy uncle Alex Chew, both till the land to create this flourishing garden. Here you can saviour fruits like blue pea with honey, papaya with Chinese tea, passion fruits, bitter gould, spices like curry leaves, banana, sugar cane, soon may be wild plants like rongat Ali, etc
Such a pretty garden, we walk by it every day on our way to work. It is fantastic to see that some people work hard for the community
Sugar cane, lime and even chicken!
